    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 7th level, Your ability to hold to precious life becomes stronger, as your cursed bloodline will not allow you to die. Once per turn, when you cast a Fujou clan Hijutsu, you recover hit points equal to the jutsu's rank (D=2, C=4, B=6, A=8, S=10). Starting at 18th levels, the hit points regained by this feature are doubled.</p>",
